><TYPE_CONTRACT CTYPE="SERVICES"/><SHORT_DESCR><P>Coventry City Council’s commercial waste service are looking to install on-board weighing technology on the back of all of their current fleet of refuse collection vehicles.</P><P>Due to the age of the current fleet we are looking to replace the entire lifting mechanism of the back of all vehicles (8 in total).</P><P>The new lifting mechanism will need to be fitted to the commercial fleet in a rolling program to ensure service continuity.</P></SHORT_DESCR><VAL_TOTAL CURRENCY="GBP">125000.00</VAL_TOTAL><NO_LOT_DIVISION/><OBJECT_DESCR ITEM="1"><CPV_ADDITIONAL><CPV_CODE CODE="34114000"/></CPV_ADDITIONAL><CPV_ADDITIONAL><CPV_CODE CODE="34144510"/></CPV_ADDITIONAL><CPV_ADDITIONAL><CPV_CODE CODE="34200000"/></CPV_ADDITIONAL><CPV_ADDITIONAL><CPV_CODE CODE="34224000"/></CPV_ADDITIONAL><CPV_ADDITIONAL><CPV_CODE CODE="34224200"/></CPV_ADDITIONAL><CPV_ADDITIONAL><CPV_CODE CODE="34300000"/></CPV_ADDITIONAL><CPV_ADDITIONAL><CPV_CODE CODE="42413500"/></CPV_ADDITIONAL><n2016:NUTS CODE="UKG33"/><MAIN_SITE><P>Coventry.</P></MAIN_SITE><SHORT_DESCR><P>Open procedure to select 1 supplier for vehicle lift replacement on 9 vehicles.</P></SHORT_DESCR><AC><AC_QUALITY><AC_CRITERION>Technical and professional ability</AC_CRITERION><AC_WEIGHTING>4 %</AC_WEIGHTING></AC_QUALITY><AC_QUALITY><AC_CRITERION>Maintenance and method statement</AC_CRITERION><AC_WEIGHTING>5 %</AC_WEIGHTING></AC_QUALITY><AC_QUALITY><AC_CRITERION>Implementation method statement</AC_CRITERION><AC_WEIGHTING>6 %</AC_WEIGHTING></AC_QUALITY><AC_QUALITY><AC_CRITERION>Interface with AMCS system</AC_CRITERION><AC_WEIGHTING>5 %</AC_WEIGHTING></AC_QUALITY><AC_COST><AC_CRITERION>Existing vehicles</AC_CRITERION><AC_WEIGHTING>70 %</AC_WEIGHTING></AC_COST><AC_COST><AC_CRITERION>Additional vehicles</AC_CRITERION><AC_WEIGHTING>10 %</AC_WEIGHTING></AC_COST></AC><NO_OPTIONS/><NO_EU_PROGR_RELATED/><INFO_ADD><P>This is a one-off procurement in respect of the Councils commercial waste services to update its 9 vehicles as part of a modernisation programme. It is envisaged that in future, new vehicles purchased will be supplied with lifts where there is an on-board weighting facility. This contract was awarded under contract reference 6650 and not 5542.</P></INFO_ADD></OBJECT_DESCR></OBJECT_CONTRACT><PROCEDURE><PT_OPEN/><CONTRACT_COVERED_GPA/><NOTICE_NUMBER_OJ>2017/S 247-517662</NOTICE_NUMBER_OJ></PROCEDURE><AWARD_CONTRACT ITEM="1"><TITLE><P>COV — Bin Lifts with On-Board Weighing Capacity for Existing Refuse Vehicles</P></TITLE><AWARDED_CONTRACT><DATE_CONCLUSION_CONTRACT>2019-11-06</DATE_CONCLUSION_CONTRACT><TENDERS><NB_TENDERS_RECEIVED>4</NB_TENDERS_RECEIVED><NB_TENDERS_RECEIVED_SME>2</NB_TENDERS_RECEIVED_SME><NB_TENDERS_RECEIVED_OTHER_EU>0</NB_TENDERS_RECEIVED_OTHER_EU><NB_TENDERS_RECEIVED_NON_EU>0</NB_TENDERS_RECEIVED_NON_EU><NB_TENDERS_RECEIVED_EMEANS>4</NB_TENDERS_RECEIVED_EMEANS></TENDERS><CONTRACTORS><NO_AWARDED_TO_GROUP/><CONTRACTOR><ADDRESS_CONTRACTOR><OFFICIALNAME>Vehicle Weighing Solutions Ltd</OFFICIALNAME><ADDRESS>Unit 5 Southview Park, Marsack Street</ADDRESS><TOWN>Caversham</TOWN><POSTAL_CODE>RG4 5AF</POSTAL_CODE><COUNTRY VALUE="UK"/><n2016:NUTS CODE="UKG33"/></ADDRESS_CONTRACTOR><SME/></CONTRACTOR></CONTRACTORS><VALUES><VAL_ESTIMATED_TOTAL CURRENCY="GBP">350000.00</VAL_ESTIMATED_TOTAL><VAL_TOTAL CURRENCY="GBP">125000.00</VAL_TOTAL></VALUES></AWARDED_CONTRACT></AWARD_CONTRACT><COMPLEMENTARY_INFO><INFO_ADD><P>Contract value of 125 000 GBP is for existing vehicles and provision is made both within the award criteria and the contract itself for future vehicles to have this equipment fitted, using this arrangement.</P></INFO_ADD><ADDRESS_REVIEW_BODY><OFFICIALNAME>Coventry City Council</OFFICIALNAME><TOWN>Coventry</TOWN><COUNTRY VALUE="UK"/></ADDRESS_REVIEW_BODY><DATE_DISPATCH_NOTICE>2020-01-10</DATE_DISPATCH_NOTICE></COMPLEMENTARY_INFO></F03_2014></FORM_SECTION></TED_EXPORT>